nodes.text: Wiley was a male wokling who lived on the forest moon of Endor. He was the son of Lumat and Zephee and the brother of Latara and Nippet.

Wiley was one of six 8-inch plush woklings made by Kenner based upon the six woklings seen in Return of the Jedi. While the character names of Malani, Nippet, and Wiley were established prior in the Ewoks television series, the other three—Mookiee, Leeni, and Gwig—have yet to be attributed to their respective characters seen in Return of the Jedi.
